This class represents a quality measurement for the current simulation, including a distance function and one or more experimental data sets.

This class may listen to changes in some user interface (whether it is a graphical or a command line interface). In order to avoid cyclic changes of its QualityMeasure, there is no set method for this property. If a QualityMeasurement receives a PropertyChangeEvent, it reacts to the following kinds of property names:

Property Expectation
distance change of the QualityMeasure
measurements adding/removing an experimental data set
